title: Unemployment rate in Brunei Darussalam 2019
summary: In general Unemployment rate has rose over the Year.
Unemployment rate is roughly constant from 2006 to 2008, gradually increasing from 2008 to 2009, roughly constant from 2009 to 2011, and lastly roughly increasing from 2011 to 2012.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2008 and 2009.
Maximum Unemployment rate, about 6.9 was reported at Year 2012
The lowest Unemployment rate, of value 5.62 was reported at Year 2007
